{"tid":853713,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有 IU 辦不到的風格！新歌 MV 預告片夢幻又俏皮","createTime":"2018-10-08T21:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T17:24:48.000Z","uid":34643,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fccdb43760702f6f65d1b723bab89d6332eb8de5","tid":853713,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T21:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_07a050d47d9a417f854fdb4e166a6739/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-08/110042-663127.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_07a050d47d9a417f854fdb4e166a6739%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-08%2F110042-663127.png&h=b20c55bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近幾年 IU 的主打歌經常走感性成熟路線，沒想到出道十週年的紀念新歌反而超級可愛！<br />\n<br />\nIU 在今天（8 日）公開了十週年驚喜新歌 &ldquo;BBIBBI&rdquo; 的 MV 預告片，雖然只有短短 20 秒，但在這支由曾和 EXO、Zico、Red Velvet⋯⋯等歌手合作過的 VM Project 操刀的影片裡，恰到好處的豐富色彩、獨特音效立刻讓人留下深刻印象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5Eo9fFVRM-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5Eo9fFVRM-g&d=CibHFg8IZnIlajm27DXBW54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=97182e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5Eo9fFVRM-g</a><br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;BBIBBI&rdquo; 是 IU 出道後首度嘗試的 alternative R&amp;B 樂風，由她親自作詞並和寫過 &ldquo;Leon&rdquo;、&rdquo;Palette&rdquo; 等歌的作曲家李宗勳再度攜手。她不僅為此挑戰了雷鬼頭造型，也變換了好幾種色調鮮明可愛的裝扮，最後一句 &ldquo;I Don&rsquo;t Believe It&rdquo; 也讓人更好奇新歌的內容！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a4266f26137872b4efc8848aa42a49e3/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-08/110042-663128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a4266f26137872b4efc8848aa42a49e3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-08%2F110042-663128.jpg&h=8a859196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;BBIBBI&rdquo; 將於 10 日傍晚正式發行，而接下來 IU 也準備展開亞洲巡迴演唱會《這當下 dlwlrma》，從釜山開始陸續巡經光州、首爾、香港、新加坡、曼谷，最後於 12 月 24 日當天來到台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5bf026eadd7494b894b4bc4fb8370482/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-08/110042-663132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5bf026eadd7494b894b4bc4fb8370482%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-08%2F110042-663132.jpg&h=101c57bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_cc61933c951b036d5d3e890ba3c57ee1/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-10-08/110042-663133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_cc61933c951b036d5d3e890ba3c57ee1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-10-08%2F110042-663133.jpg&h=87a66c18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1d0b0ef6b129bec4560de1d0283aae013adbcb2","tid":853713,"uid":214056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"今次無乜圖 算你啦"},{"pid":"bae2ab080f2efcd76565085164ee78b507639ee7","tid":853713,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1d0b0ef6b129bec4560de1d0283aae013adbcb2","tid":853713,"uid":214056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"今次無乜圖 算你啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97a3c7fd8943fcfbb7f17d1af53d76a244b169f","tid":853713,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T17:24:48.000Z","msg":"聽日就係了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}